long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension facilitates users in acquiring orders from the writerslabs website (https://writerslabs.com/). It is a straightforward and confidential application. Primarily tailored for a specific purpose, this extension is intended to be utilized privately. Its main function is to automate the process of obtaining orders. It works by monitoring changes on the order page and takes the order when one is assigned.
